& [BOS]BOD4 ~= [F:BOH]BOMALT;[F:BOH]ITMREF;[F:BOH]BOMALTTYP,
& [TBO]TBO0 ~= [F:BOH]BOMALTTYP;[F:BOH]BOMALT
